Function: HasSameOwner
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Input:  
    a, b // two pods
Output: 
    HasSameOwner // boolean, true if they share at least one controller

  for each ownerRef (*$r_a \in$*) a.ownerReferences do
      for each ownerRef (*$r_\beta \in$*) b.ownerReferences do
          if (*$r_a$*).uid = (*$r_\beta$*).uid then
              return true
          end if
      end for
  end for
  return false